text: The Audi Q5 is an SUV produced by Audi since 2008. It is based on the platform of the Audi A4 and has permanent allwheel drive, called quattro. == Engines == === Petrol === * 2.0 TFSI 132 kW (180 hp) and 155 kW (212 hp) * 3.2 FSI 199 kW (270 hp) === Diesel === * 2.0 TDI 105 kW (143 hp) and 125 kW (170 hp) * 3.0 TDI 176 kW (240 hp) Q5 Category:Sport utility vehicles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles
title: Audi Q5
